#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Service Manager</guilabel> module allows you to have an "
"overview of all plugins of the &kde; Daemon, also referred to as &kde; "
"Services. Generally, there are two types of service:"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Zerbitzu kudeatzailea</guilabel> moduluak &kde; daimonaren, &kde; "
"zerbitzuak bezala ere ezaguna, plugin guztien ikuspegi orokor bat izateko "
"aukera ematen dizu. Oro har, bi zerbitzu mota daude:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:37
#, no-c-format
msgid "Load-on-Demand Services"
msgstr "Eskatu ahala zamatzen diren zerbitzuak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is a list of available &kde; services which will be started on demand. "
"They are only listed for convenience, as you cannot manipulate these "
"services."
msgstr ""
"Hori da eskatu ahala abiaraziko diren &kde; zerbitzuen zerrenda bat. "
"Erosotasunagatik bakarrik daude zerrenda, zerbitzu horiek ezin baitira "
"manipulatu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "Startup Services"
msgstr "Abioko zerbitzuak"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This shows all &kde; services that can be loaded on &kde; startup. Services "
"checked in the <guilabel>Use</guilabel> column will be invoked on next "
"startup."
msgstr ""
"Horrek &kde;ren abioan zama daitezkeen &kde; zerbitzu guztiak erakusten "
"ditu. <guilabel>Erabili</guilabel> zutabea markatuta duten zerbitzuak "
"hurrengo abioan deituko dira."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Be careful with deactivation of unknown services: some services are vital "
"for &kde;; do not deactivate services if you do not know what you are doing."
msgstr ""
"Kontuz zerbitzu ezezagunak desaktibatzearekin: zerbitzu batzuk &kde;rentzat "
"funtsezkoak dira; ez desaktibatu zerbitzuak zertan ari zaren ez badakizu."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the <guilabel>Status</guilabel> of a service, select it in the "
"list. Then you can use the <guibutton>Start</guibutton> and <guibutton>Stop</"
"guibutton> to change the status of a service from <guilabel>Not running</"
"guilabel> to <guilabel>Running</guilabel> and vice versa."
msgstr ""
"Zerbitzu baten <guilabel>Egoera</guilabel> aldatzeko, zerrendan hauta ezazu. "
"Ondoren <guibutton>Abiarazi</guibutton> eta <guibutton>Geldiarazi</"
"guibutton> erabil ditzakezu zerbitzuaren egoera <guilabel>Ez da exekutatzen "
"ari</guilabel>tik <guilabel>Exekutatzen</guilabel> egoerara aldatzeko, eta "
"alderantziz."
